pageContext.claim: “I don't know what the fuss is all about. I think we did extremely well. And I think the press makes up the, look, it's fake news. And people understand. I think the press largely makes up a lot of the fuss about a lot of things. And I'm not talking about everything.”
pageContext.analysis: Mainstream media organizations may make mistakes, which are corrected, but they do not make up news.
